  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Site Supervisor (Civil/Infrastructure)",
  "description": "<h2>Site Supervisor (Civil/Infrastructure)</h2>\n<p><strong>Visit https://ourengineers.com</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate and supervise subcontractors and in-house workers.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with project requirements and scope.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with safety personnel for health and safety adherence.</li>\n  <li>Support Project Managers and Engineers in executing permanent and temporary works.</li>\n  <li>Verify installations align with construction drawings.</li>\n  <li>Maintain work quality within set deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Conduct equipment, material, and routine inspections.</li>\n  <li>Monitor work progress and quality.</li>\n  <li>Participate in daily toolbox meetings and provide clear instructions.</li>\n  <li>Update work progress records, ensure housekeeping, and prepare reports.</li>\n  <li>Manage site manpower planning and usage.</li>\n  <li>Perform other assigned duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Job Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of experience in civil engineering.</li>\n  <li>Certificate in Pavement Construction &amp; Maintenance is advantageous.</li>\n  <li>Proactive, self-motivated, team-oriented, strong problem-solving, and communication skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Additional Remarks:</h3>\n<p>Hands-on experience is preferred.</p>",
